Privacy Policy for Lotto Peak

Effective Date: [October 29, 2025]

Lotto Peak (‚Äúthe Application‚Äù, ‚ÄúApp‚Äù, ‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, or ‚Äúus‚Äù) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how our Application handles user data and clarifies that we do not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive information from our users.
____________________________________________________

1. Information We Collect

Lotto Peak is a FREE, offline number combination generator and analyzer.
We do not collect, store, process, or share any personally identifiable information (such as your name, email address, or location).

The App operates primarily offline, and all main features work without an internet connection.

The following limited information may be handled locally on your device:

    * User Preferences: Selected lotto game type or generated number preferences (stored locally only).
    * Winning Number History: Historical results or generated combinations saved locally on your device.

These data remain within your device and are never transmitted to any external server or third party.
_____________________________________________________

2. Advertising and Third-Party Services

Lotto Peak is a FREE application supported by advertisements.
We may use third-party advertising providers, such as Google AdMob, to display ads within the app. These third-party partners may collect limited, non-personal data such as:

    * Device information (e.g., model, operating system)
    * General location (e.g., city-level)
    * Advertising ID (used for ad personalization and analytics)

These data are handled according to the respective third party‚Äôs privacy policies and are not stored or controlled by Lotto Peak.

You can learn more about how Google manages data in advertising here:
üîó https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

You may choose to disable personalized advertising by adjusting your device settings:

    * Settings ‚Üí Google ‚Üí Ads ‚Üí Opt out of Ads Personalization

______________________________________________________

3. Permissions Used

Lotto Peak may request certain permissions to ensure proper functionality.
All permissions are used solely for their stated purpose and never to collect personal data.

    * Storage Access: Allows saving and retrieving lotto number combinations and analytics locally.
    * Internet Access: Used only for displaying ads and loading ad content.

______________________________________________________

4. How We Use Information

Since Lotto Peak does not collect personal data, there is no sharing, selling, or misuse of such information.
All calculations and analytics (e.g., generating random combinations, ranking top winning numbers, analyzing historical data) occur entirely on your device.

______________________________________________________

5. Data Security

All local data (such as generated combinations or winning number histories) are stored only within your device‚Äôs app storage.
No data are transmitted externally.
You may delete the app at any time to remove all stored data permanently.

______________________________________________________

6. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Lotto Peak is designed for general audiences and may be used by individuals of all ages.
However, we do not knowingly collect or store any personal data from children under 13 years old (or under the legal age in your country).
If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has interacted with ads that collect data, please review the privacy policy of the respective ad provider.

